'''第31届学院奖颁奖典礼'''于1959年4月6日在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]{{link-en|雷电华潘太及斯剧院|Pantages Theatre (Hollywood)}}举行，[[杰瑞·刘易斯|杰瑞·刘易斯]]、{{le|莫特·索尔|Mort Sahl}}、{{link-en|托尼·兰德尔|Tony Randall}}、[[鲍勃·霍普|鲍勃·霍普]]、[[大卫·尼文|大卫·尼文]]和[[劳伦斯·奥利弗|劳伦斯·奥利弗]]共同担任主持人。

文森特·明尼利执导的《[[金粉世界|金粉世界]]》惊人地在全部9个提名中胜出，打破了[[第12届奥斯卡金像奖|第12届]]中《[[乱世佳人|乱世佳人]]》获奖8项的纪录成为最大赢家。不过这个纪录也只保持了一年，因为[[第32届奥斯卡金像奖|第32届]]时[[威廉·惠勒|威廉·惠勒]]执导的《[[賓漢|賓漢]]》将夺得11项奖<ref name="Oscars1960">{{Cite web| url= http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/32nd-winners.html| title= The 32nd Academy Awards (1960) Nominees and Winners| accessdate= 2011-08-21| work= oscars.org| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110706094204/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/32nd-winners.html| archivedate= 2011-07-06| deadurl= no}}</ref>，该纪录至今仍未打破，仅有两次被追平（包括[[第70屆奧斯卡金像獎|第70届]]的《[[泰坦尼克号_(1997年电影)|鐵達尼號]]》和[[第76屆奧斯卡金像獎|第76届]]的《[[指环王：王者归来|魔戒三部曲：王者再臨]]》）<ref>[http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/news/1998/03/24/1998-03-24__titanic___rides_huge_oscar_.html 'TITANIC ' RIDES HUGE OSCAR WAVE SNAGS 11 AWARDS, TIES ALL-TIME RECORD] ''NY Daily News'' Retrieved 2010-1-1</ref><ref name="Oscars1998">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/70th-winners.html |title=The 70th Academy Awards (1998) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2011-11-19 |work=oscars.org |archive-date=2013-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224032304/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/70th-winners.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.rte.ie/news/2004/0301/oscars.html Lord Of The Rings garners 11 Oscars] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rte.ie/news/2004/0301/oscars.html |date=20121024060832 }} ''RTE News'' Retrieved 2010-1-1</ref><ref name="Oscars2004">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/76th-winners.html |title=The 76th Academy Awards (2004) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2011-11-20 |work=oscars.org |archive-date=2012-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120929190645/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/76th-winners.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过《金粉世界》9项提名全部获奖这一情况下一次再重现则是29年后的[[第60届奥斯卡金像奖|第60届]]，由[[贝纳尔多·贝托鲁奇|贝纳尔多·贝托鲁奇]]执导的《[[末代皇帝_(電影)|末代皇帝]]》也是9项提名全部获奖<ref name="Oscars1988">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/60th-winners.html |title=The 60th Academy Awards (1988) Nominees and Winners |work=oscars.org |access-date=2013-05-24 |archive-date=2014-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141001073353/https://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/60th-winners.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。并且这两部电影也是少数未获任何演员奖提名但却拿下[[学院奖最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]的作品，其以这一特别情况创下的获奖数量最高纪录要一直到《[[指环王：王者归来|魔戒三部曲：王者再臨]]》才被打破<ref name="Oscars2004" />。

